{"tid":2129457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌轟政府經濟凌駕抗疫","createTime":"2020-07-28T15:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T15:06:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a14673cb34f4da008130097a3f2031e8d60d23","tid":2129457,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/2PNRMWLRVV5PD4WYQJPY5LRGMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2F2PNRMWLRVV5PD4WYQJPY5LRGMA%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD9w%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=8c665851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2F2PNRMWLRVV5PD4WYQJPY5LRGMA%2F&h=c7480911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/2PNRMWLRVV5PD4WYQJPY5LRGMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌轟政府經濟凌駕抗疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6Jxi4HvDrvp0phLUiHPxa_C82D0=/640x437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FYGOBPPOMAXWMLRQHUSZITS5BQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6Jxi4HvDrvp0phLUiHPxa_C82D0%3D%2F640x437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFYGOBPPOMAXWMLRQHUSZITS5BQ.jpg&h=421622a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許樹昌<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多名政府抗疫顧問本月初已指本港第三波疫潮或源於獲豁免檢疫者，政府前日宣佈明起暫停客船及無在港處理貨物裝卸的貨船船員換班。政府抗疫督導委員會專家顧問、中大醫學院呼吸系統學講座教授許樹昌昨接受商台訪問時稱，一直與食衞局長陳肇始有交流，但承認政府收緊豁免檢疫者防疫安排並非單靠食衞局決定，被問到是否反映政府商務考慮凌駕公共衞生，許表示認同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料第三波疫潮會持續<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭卸責 推張建宗做炮灰<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌稱，政府7月8日已要求抵港機組人員留樣本檢測，當中發現50多名確診者，認為防疫措施方向正確。............................................<br />\n<br />\n許續指醫院非緊急服務暫停後，臨床醫護人手足以應付病人增加情況，但若確診個案持續上升，........................................."}]}